td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Article 1(1) and Article 1(2)(a) of Council Directive 93/42/EEC of 14 June 1993 concerning medical devices (
OJ 1993 L 169, p. 1
), as amended by Directive 2007/47/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 5 September 2007 (
OJ 2007 L 247, p. 21
) (‘Directive 93/42’).
